serializableData.oldContent: Free Spins round total win in the history contains the whole win of the cycle.

The maximum win amount is limited to {0}x bet in both base game and free spins. If the total win of a round reaches {1}x bet the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining free spins are forfeited.

On the left side of the screen in landscape mode and top of the screen in portrait mode, next to each reel, there is a UFO with different awards on it that can be won through the feature. Possible awards are:
Malfunction voids all pays and plays.
- MINOR - A direct MONEY award of 50x total bet that will be collected at the end of the feature.
When buying the COSMIC RESPINS feature the round will start with 6 MONEY symbols with random value.
Free Spins round win is awarded to the player after the round completes.
Special reels are in play during the feature that have more stacked WILD symbols on reels 2, 3 and 4.
At the end of the round all amounts from all MONEY symbols along with unlocked UFO awards are added together and paid.
The COSMIC RESPINS feature can be instantly triggered from the base game by buying it for 100x current total bet.
All symbols pay from left to right on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost reel.
Hit 6 or more MONEY symbols to trigger the COSMIC RESPINS feature.
WILD symbol appears on all reels in the base game and FREE SPINS feature.
All wins are multiplied by base bet.
The RTP of the game when using "BUY BONUS" is {0}%
This is the WILD symbol and substitutes for all symbols except for SCATTER and MONEY symbol.
Free Spin wins are added to the payline win.
All values are expressed as actual wins in coins.
High volatility games pay out less often on average but the chance to hit big wins in a short time span is higher
- Direct money award - Randomly between 10x and 250x total bet.
The theoretical RTP of this game is {0}%
When winning on multiple paylines, all wins are added to the total win.
Only the highest win is paid per winning combination on the same payline.

When the feature starts, the base game reels are replaced with special reels containing only MONEY symbols and blanks. During the round, only MONEY symbols or blanks can stop on any position on the grid.
It appears on all reels in the base game and FREE SPINS feature.
At the start of the round, the MONEY symbols hit in the base game will move to the end of the screen, to the right in landscape mode and to the bottom in portrait mode.
- GRAND - A direct MONEY award of 2,500x total bet that will be collected at the end of the feature.
At every spin each MONEY symbol takes a random value from a pre-defined set up to 100x total bet.
- MINI - A direct MONEY award of 20x total bet that will be collected at the end of the feature.

After stopping, hit symbols move towards the end of the screen, and the UFO next to it opens one more empty spot, in it's direction extending the number of possible positions on the grid, up to a maximum of 2 spots on each reel.
The round ends when there are no more respins remaining or all the positions on the grid, including extensions are fully filled.
If all spots on one of the reels gets filled by MONEY symbols, the award of the UFO next to it is unlocked.
- Free spins - A random number of free spins from 10 to 100. Winning this award will trigger the FREE SPINS round with the won number of spins after the current feature ends.
This is the MONEY symbol. It can appear on all reels.
The round starts with 3 respins. All symbols that hit after each respin remain on the screen until the end of the round. Whenever any symbol hits, the number of respins is reset back to 3.
- MAJOR - A direct MONEY award of 250x total bet that will be collected at the end of the feature.
Hit 3, 4 or 5 SCATTER symbols to trigger 10, 20 or 50 free spins respectively. The FREE SPINS round can also be won in the COSMIC RESPINS feature from an UFO award.
SPACE and ENTER buttons on the keyboard can be used to start and stop the spin.
- Multiplier - A multiplier from 2x to 50x that will apply to all MONEY symbols under the awarded UFO at the end of the feature.
Hit 3, 4 or 5 SCATTER symbols during the round to retrigger the feature and get 10, 20 or 50 additional free spins.
The RTP of the game when using "BUY RESPINS" is {0}%

serializableData._text: Nemokam sukim bendras laimjimas istorijoje laiko viso ciklo laimjim.

Didiausia laimjimo suma tiek pagrindiniame aidime, tiek nemokamuose sukimuose yra {0}x statymo. Jei bendra raundo laimjimo suma pasiekia {1}x statymo, raundas i karto baigiasi, laimjimas teikiamas, o visi lik nemokami sukimai anuliuojami.
Kairje ekrano pusje gulsiu reimu ir ekrano viruje staiu reimu, alia kiekvieno bgno, yra UFO su vairiais apdovanojimais, kuriuos galima laimti per funkcij. Galimi ie apdovanojimai:
Gedimai anuliuoja visus imokjimus ar aidimus.
- MINOR - tiesioginis 50x viso statymo dydio PINIG apdovanojimas, kuris bus surinktas funkcijos pabaigoje.
sigijus funkcij KOSMINI PAKARTOTINI SUKIM, raundas prasids su 6 atsitiktins verts PINIG simboliais.
Pasibaigus raundui nemokam sukim laimjimas suteikiamas aidjui.
Funkcijos metu aidiami specials bgnai, kuriuose ant 2, 3 ir 4 bgn yra daugiau grupini WILD simboli.
Raundo pabaigoje visos sumos, gautos i vis PINIG simboli, kartu su atrakintais UFO apdovanojimais sudedamos ir imokamos.
KOSMINI PAKARTOTINI SUKIM funkcij galite i karto suaktyvinti i pagrindinio aidimo, nusipirk j u 100x dabartinio viso statymo.
Visi simboliai imokami i kairs  dein ant gretim bgn pradedant nuo kairiosios puss.
Isukite 6 ar daugiau PINIG simboli, kad bt suaktyvinta KOSMINI PAKARTOTINI SUKIM funkcija.
WILD simbolis rodomas ant vis pagrindinio aidimo ir NEMOKAM SUKIM funkcijos bgn.
Visi laimjimai padauginami i bazinio statymo.
Tai WILD simbolis, kuris pakeiia visus simbolius, iskyrus SCATTER ir PINIG simbolius.
Nemokam sukim laimjimai pridedami prie imokjimo linijos laimjimo.
Visi laimjimai ireikti kaip tikri laimjimai monetomis.
Didelio kintamumo aidimai vidutinikai imoka maiau, taiau galimyb laimti dideles sumas i ma sukim skaiiaus kur kas didesn
- Tiesioginis pinig prizas - atsitiktinai nuo 10x iki 250x viso statymo.
Jei laimima keliose eilse, visi laimjimai pridedami  bendr laimjim.
Tik didiausias laimjimas imokamas laiminiai kombinacijai toje paioje imok eilutje.

Prasidjus funkcijai, pagrindinio aidimo bgnai pakeiiami specialiais bgnais, kuriuose yra tik PINIG simboliai ir tuti simboliai. Raundo metu bet kurioje tinklelio pozicijoje gali sustoti tik PINIG simboliai arba tuti langeliai.
Jis rodomas visuose pagrindinio aidimo ir NEMOKAM SUKIM funkcijos bgnuose.
Raundo pradioje pagrindinio aidimo metu isukti PINIG simboliai persikels  ekrano gal, guliu reimu -  dein, o staiu reimu -  apai.
- GRAND - tiesioginis 2500x viso statymo dydio PINIG apdovanojimas, kuris bus surinktas funkcijos pabaigoje.
Kiekvieno sukimo metu kiekvienas PINIG simbolis gyja atsitiktin vert i i anksto nustatytos iki 100x viso statymo.
- MINI - 20x viso statymo tiesioginis PINIG apdovanojimas, kuris bus surinktas funkcijos pabaigoje.
Sustabdius, isukti simboliai juda link ekrano galo, o alia esantis UFO atveria dar vien tui viet, jo kryptimi ipleiant galim pozicij tinklelyje skaii iki maksimalaus 2 viet skaiiaus kiekviename bgne.
Raundas baigiasi, kai nebelieka joki pakartotini sukim arba visos tinklelio pozicijos, skaitant pratsimus, yra visikai upildytos.
Jei viename i bgn visas vietas upildo PINIG simboliai, atrakinamas alia esantis UFO apdovanojimas.
- Nemokami sukimai - atsitiktinis nemokam sukim skaiius nuo 10 iki 100. Laimjus  apdovanojim, pasibaigus dabartinei funkcijai, bus suaktyvintas NEMOKAM SUKIM raundas su laimtu sukim skaiiumi.
Tai PINIG simbolis. Jis gali bti rodomas visuose bgnuose.

Raundas prasideda nuo 3 pakartotini sukim. Visi simboliai, kurie patenka po kiekvieno pakartotinio sukimo, lieka ekrane iki raundo pabaigos. Kiekvien kart, kai isukamas bet kuris simbolis, pakartotini sukim skaiius grinamas  3.
- MAJOR - tiesioginis 250x viso statymo dydio PINIG apdovanojimas, kuris bus surinktas funkcijos pabaigoje.
Isukite 3, 4 arba 5 SCATTER simbolius, kad jungtumte atitinkamai 10, 20 arba 50 nemokam sukim. NEMOKAM SUKIM raund taip pat galima laimti per KOSMINI PAKARTOTINI SUKIM funkcij i UFO apdovanojimo.
TARPO ir ENTER klaviatros mygtukai gali bti naudojami, kad paleist ar stabdyt sukim.
- Daugiklis - daugiklis nuo 2x iki 50x, kuris bus taikomas visiems PINIG simboliams, esantiems po suteiktu UFO, funkcijos pabaigoje.
Raundo metu isukite 3, 4 arba 5 SCATTER simbolius, kad pakartotinai suaktyvintumte funkcij ir gautumte 10, 20 arba 50 papildom nemokam sukim.

Galimos verts yra: 0.375x, 0.5x, 0.625x, 0.75x, 1 x, 1.25x, 2x, 2.5x, 3.75x, 5x, 10x, 20x, 25x, 40x, 50x arba 100x bendro statymo.
